{"tid":2121409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街市檔主懶理新例拉低口罩 街坊憂噴毒避光顧","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T09:57:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12afbf167c5ac272b0c28fbd75e2ed6ec0c9fd1b","tid":2121409,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/GLBOTUYFRKFRW6PPJI6H7MZVKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FGLBOTUYFRKFRW6PPJI6H7MZVKU%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCHqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=01de70a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FGLBOTUYFRKFRW6PPJI6H7MZVKU%2F&h=1e7f4461\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/GLBOTUYFRKFRW6PPJI6H7MZVKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，後知後覺的港府終在昨天修例，公佈會強制任何人士於室內公眾地方均須佩戴口罩，違者最高會被罰款5,000元港幣。《蘋果》今到九龍灣及牛頭角視察，發現大多市民都有遵從「口罩令」；至於牛頭角街市就有攤主將口罩拉下，有市民指因為擔心他們叫賣時會將口水濺到貨物，所以買餸會特意避開這些檔販<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"674ca0cc8470e3978e0d5d294cd17f07a8456cdf","tid":2121409,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"措施生效第一日，在牛頭角及九龍灣一帶的商場，顧客及商戶都有遵從「口罩令」，相當自律，只有一名途經德福商場外有蓋處的中年女士沒有佩戴口罩。不過，法例並未有訂明這些「半室外地帶」是否同受規管，商場保安指自己亦不清楚該處到底是否屬室內，稱要待上級的清晰指示。"},{"pid":"799573287b53f500a42fe5131d5902c905053317","tid":2121409,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"不過，門庭如市的牛頭角街市，就有至少三、四名攤販都將口罩拉至下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，未知有否違反「口罩令」。《蘋果》記者詢問其中一名將口罩拉下的魚販，他隨即將口罩拉回鼻頭上，並指「而家戴返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，旁邊的職員則連忙向記者稱「我哋知㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，又表示「以後都會戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。"},{"pid":"f1985ec30d946e4a39eb1e782de5a5fef320d44a","tid":2121409,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"正苦千金請個PR番來<br />\n<br />\n可以搵佢地宣傳戴罩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8ec537af8b7121bf9ecd37815720b0801d4f83","tid":2121409,"uid":126226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"改左去超市買 感覺安全D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461f461e7d1cd7819551570c6a82f1417278896","tid":2121409,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8ec537af8b7121bf9ecd37815720b0801d4f83","tid":2121409,"uid":126226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"改左去超市買 感覺安全D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"誠哥又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bde4aa86d041ce0742cfc4d5fc39bf72804a26","tid":2121409,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"以前有時見到有啲廚師戴個只係遮口鼻嘅膠,點解咁少廚師用?取代口罩(廚房)得唔得?"}]}